name: Candy Cone
description:
Oh what pretty pixels in yummy colors! Move your mouse or finger to guide the fountain. Press down to toggle the movement. 

Collect this interactive NFT from Dr Abstract the Founder of ZIM and all these candy pixel sprinkles are yours!

Dr Abstract is the inaugural member of the Gadget Minters.  To find out more please visit https://zimjs.com/gadgetminters and https://zimjs.com/nft for info on making interactive NFTs with ZIM.
